examples.en: The teacher often flogged the students.
The sailors were flogged for attempting a mutiny.
He was publicly flogged and humiliated.
examples.ru: Он подвергся публичной порке и унижению.

examples.en: Every young and healthy feeling flogged and starved down. (Ch. Dickens)
examples.ru: Любое здоровое проявление чувств осуждалось и подавлялось.
